用户问陈皮冷藏好...(String), 2299(Integer), 2543(Integer), {"charStart":2299,"fileName":"04_陈皮储存养护指南.md","groupId":2,"charEnd":2543,"documentId":6,"source":"minio://argus-rag-documents/groups/2/users/1/41e12c86f749417283107e3c75a23cc2.md","sectionPath":"","chunkStrategy":"structure-aware-token-budget-v1","chunkIndex":8}(String), 2026-06-19T16:59:09.120590400(LocalDateTime), 2026-06-19T16:59:09.120590400(LocalDateTime), 6(Long), 2(Long), 9(Integer), 的位置。若短期临时低温保存，必须做好防潮、防串味和回温处理。

